title: Flight Simulator 2020 - Addon spotlight  - Great wall of China
description:
In this addon spotlight we are going to look at the great wall of China and specifically the Mutianyu Section. The addon has been released earlier this month but I just spotted it on flightsim.to and thought it would be nice to create a video about it. The wall is pretty detailed and even includes a cable car which brings visitors to the top of the wall.

If you want to also add the great wall of China to MSFS 2020 download it from the site below:
https://flightsim.to/file/18761/the-great-wall-of-china-mutianyu-section
